             was indicted for <rs id="t18000917-72-off387" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000917-72-off387" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000917-72-off387" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
