                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-72-off387 t18000917-72-cd388"></join>, four sheets, value 3l. a counterpane value 38s. two towels, value 2s. and two nigh-caps, value 2s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000917-72-victim757" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Freeman
